				</row>
			</thead>
			<tbody>
                            <row>
				<entry><ulink url="http://bugs.cloud.com/show_bug.cgi?id=10680">10680</ulink></entry>
                                <entry>Changing xen.guest.network.device in global configuration will now change existing hosts.</entry>
                            </row>
                            <row>
				<entry> many </entry>
                                <entry>Template and volume download functionality is much more reliable.</entry>
                            </row>
                            <row>
				<entry><ulink url="http://bugs.cloud.com/show_bug.cgi?id=10844">10844</ulink></entry>
                                <entry>The outbound network traffic of statically NATed guests will correctly show the additional static NAT IP as the source.</entry>
                            </row>
                            <row>
				<entry><ulink url="http://bugs.cloud.com/show_bug.cgi?id=10489">10489</ulink></entry>
                                <entry>API calls to list large numbers of VMs have improved performance.</entry>
                            </row>
                            <row>
				<entry><ulink url="http://bugs.cloud.com/show_bug.cgi?id=11027">11027</ulink></entry>
                                <entry>Idle management servers will no longer lose a connection to MySQL.</entry>
